<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>403 - Akses Ditolak</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;600&display=swap');

*{
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  box-sizing:border-box;
  font-family:'Orbitron',sans-serif;
}

body{
  height:100vh;
  background:#050505;
  overflow:hidden;
  color:#9eff00;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  text-align:center;
}

/* Neon grid background */
body::before{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;
  width:200%;
  height:200%;
  background:
    repeating-linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      rgba(0,255,0,0.05) 0px,
      rgba(0,255,0,0.05) 2px,
      transparent 2px,
      transparent 80px
    ),
    repeating-linear-gradient(
      0deg,
      rgba(0,255,0,0.05) 0px,
      rgba(0,255,0,0.05) 2px,
      transparent 2px,
      transparent 80px
    );
  animation: moveGrid 10s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes moveGrid{
  from{ transform:translate(0,0); }
  to{ transform:translate(-80px,-80px); }
}

/* Snake glow aura */
.snake-glow{
  position:absolute;
  width:600px;
  height:600px;
  background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,255,0,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
  filter:blur(80px);
  animation:pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse{
  0%,100%{ transform:scale(1); opacity:0.5; }
  50%{ transform:scale(1.2); opacity:0.9; }
}

.card{
  position:relative;
  padding:60px 80px;
  border:1px solid #1aff00;
  border-radius:16px;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.65);
  box-shadow:
    0 0 20px #1aff00,
    inset 0 0 30px rgba(0,255,0,0.2);
  z-index:2;
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
}

h1{
  font-size:90px;
  letter-spacing:8px;
  text-shadow:0 0 20px #39ff14;
}

h2{
  margin-top:10px;
  font-weight:400;
  letter-spacing:4px;
  color:#ccffcc;
}

p{
  margin:25px 0 40px;
  color:#b6ff9e;
  font-size:15px;
  line-height:1.6;
}

.btn{
  padding:14px 40px;
  border:1px solid #39ff14;
  background:transparent;
  color:#9eff00;
  text-decoration:none;
  border-radius:30px;
  transition:0.3s;
  box-shadow:0 0 12px #39ff14;
}

.btn:hover{
  background:#39ff14;
  color:#000;
  box-shadow:0 0 30px #39ff14;
}

/* subtle snake pattern */
.snake-pattern{
  position:absolute;
  inset:0;
  background-image:url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/asfalt-light.png');
  opacity:0.05;
  z-index:1;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="snake-glow"></div>
<div class="snake-pattern"></div>

<div class="card">
  <h1>403</h1>
  <h2>AKSES DITOLAK</h2>
  <p>
    Anda mencoba memasuki wilayah sistem yang tidak memiliki izin akses.<br>
    Sistem keamanan aktif. Aktivitas Anda telah dicatat.
  </p>
  <a href="/" class="btn">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
